- If the value matches, it returns the index.
- If the value at `mid` is less than the target, the search continues in the right half (adjusting `left`).
- If the value at `mid` is greater than the target, the search continues in the left half (adjusting `right`).
- If the loop ends without finding the target, it returns `-1`.

